help.COMMANDS:
Commands are tied to prefixes

(get)  { ? <sheet> <field> <value> ... }
(set)  { + <sheet> <field> <value> ... }
(del)  { - <sheet> <field> <value> ... }
(sync) { ~ <sheet> <guildID> }

[Setup your channel settings with:]
~~ <field> <value>

[Query your channel settings with:]
?? channel

[Get possible fields in a sheet with:]
?? <sheet>
